product.description:
Description

The attachments are easy to use and can be attached to most hair dryers, making them a versatile and convenient addition to your hair care routine. Made from durable materials, our comb and concentrator attachments are built to withstand daily use and provide you with long-lasting results. Upgrade your hair drying routine with our premium attachments!

Features

-Color:Assorted Color
-Material:Plastic
- Size: 12.50X7.00X5.00cm/4.91X2.75X1.97in 
- Size: 8.00X7.50X5.00cm/3.14X2.95X1.97in 

- Versatile effects: These hair dryer attachments are designed with different shapes, allowing you to create a range of different hair styles easily and precisely.
- Rich hair styles: Whether you have straight or curly hair, these hair dryer attachments are perfect for creating the hair style you want.
- Precision engineering: The hair blower attachment is carefully crafted to ensure it fits your hair dryer perfectly and won't damage your hair.
- Lasting use: Crafted from premium plastic, these hair dryer nozzles are designed to withstand high temperatures and deformation, ensuring they remain safe and durable.
- Universal use: These hair dryer concentrators are suitable for various hair dryer modes and types, making them easy to attach and remove as needed.
